{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a554fc3fd2","title":"用和平方法解决西北向题的可能性是存在的","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"a7aea7414f","index":0,"year":1949,"month":4,"day":28,"articleId":"a554fc3fd2"}],"tags":[{"id":"ae0a6697a5","name":"彭德怀","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji26","name":"毛泽东全集第26卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji26.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji26":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"b58040e679","type":"paragraph","text":"用和平方法解决西北向题的","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji26","articleId":"a554fc3fd2"},{"id":"0c93840c03","type":"paragraph","text":"可能性是存在的","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji26","articleId":"a554fc3fd2"},{"id":"600b9c349e","type":"paragraph","text":"1949年4月28日）德怀呵志假如西野方面暂时不打大仗，你可否于回陕前来中央一谈关于用和平方法解决西北的问题。看样子，此种可能性是存在的。张治中等人现在决定留平，并向我方靠拢。用和平方法解决西北问题这件事，我们或须考虑通过张治中的帮助去做。如何，盼复。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji26","articleId":"a554fc3fd2"},{"id":"922023c3cd","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji26","articleId":"a554fc3fd2"},{"id":"cd7b8eae2f","type":"paragraph","text":"印俭U德怀，即彭德怀，当时任第一野战军司令员兼致治委员。12德怀，即彭德怀，当时任第一野战军司令员兼致治委员。3]西野，指西北野湿军，1949年2月改称第一野战军。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji26","articleId":"a554fc3fd2"},{"id":"9dcdf7bbb5","type":"paragraph","text":"张治中，原任国民党军西北军致长官公署长官。1949年1月任国民党政府和平该判代表团首席代表，率代表团到北平和中共代表团进行谈判。4月15日，双方拟定“国内和平协定（最后修正案）”，4月20日国民党政府","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji26","articleId":"a554fc3fd2"}],"page":{"id":"ef67187ac8","publicationId":"maoquanji26","articleId":"a554fc3fd2","start":335,"end":335}}}},"__N_SSG":true}